text=!!!! Art i Disseny interactiu %0a%0a*[[https://monoskop.org/Computer_art | '''Monoskop. Resources to artists and publications on computer art''']]%0a%0a''Pre-Inici''%0a*[['''Bridget Riley'''->https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bridget_Riley]]: Pintora del opart%0a%0a''Inicis''%0a*[['''Frieder Nake'''->https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frieder_Nake]]%0a*[['''Charles Csuri'''->https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Csuri]]%0a*[['''Michael Noll'''->https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A._Michael_Noll]]%0a*[['''Olia Lialina'''->http://art.teleportacia.org/]]%0a*[['''Scott Snibbe'''->https://www.snibbe.com/]]%0a*[['''Jeffrey Shaw'''->https://www.jeffreyshawcompendium.com/portfolio/legible-city/]]%0a*[['''Ken Goldberg'''->https://goldberg.berkeley.edu/#A2]]%0a*[['''Christa Sommerer and Laurent Mignonneau'''->http://www.interface.ufg.ac.at/christa-laurent/]]%0a*[['''Peter Dittmers'''->https://www.canopycanopycanopy.com/contents/the-amme-talks]]%0a*[['''Myron Krueger'''->https://proyectoidis.org/myron-krueger/]]%0a*[['''Nicolas Schöffer'''->http://www.thecentreofattention.org/centre/afoundexhibition.html]]%0a*[['''Olafur Elliasson'''->https://olafureliasson.net/archive/artwork]]%0a*[['''Rosa Menkman'''->https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rosa_Menkman]]: she is an artist, art theorist, curator, glitch artist and visual artist specialising in glitch art and resolution theory%0a*[['''Vera Molnar'''->https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vera_Moln%25C3%25A1r]]: he began working with computers, where she began to create algorithmic paintings based on simple geometric shapes geometrical themes.%0a* [['''Ben Laposky'''->http://atariarchives.org/artist/sec6.php]]: Precursor de l'art electrònic a partir de enregistrar imatges creades a partir d'un osciloscopi.%0a* [['''John Whitney'''->http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Whitney_%2528animator%2529]]: Considerat un dels pares de l'animació amb l'ordinador, va realitzar projectes en el món del grafisme audiovisual amb ordinador. [["Catalog, 1961"->https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TbV7loKp69s]], [["Arabesque, 1975"->https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w7h0ppnUQhE]].%0a*[['''Herbert W. Franke'''->http://digitalartmuseum.org/franke/artworks.html]]: Precursor de l'associació del camp de la tecnologia i l'art, que ell anomenà "experimental aesthetics".I va fundar el festival d'Art Electrònic 1979, Ars electronic Linz.%0a*[['''Lillian Schwartz'''->http://vimeo.com/lillianschwartz]]%0a*[['''Roman Verostko'''->http://www.verostko.com/menu.html]]: El seu treball destaca per la utilització d'elements analogics com digitals.%0a*[['''George Legrady'''->http://www.georgelegrady.com/]]: El seu treball destaca per ser un dels pioners en la utilització de l'art electrònic per crear espais, instal·lacions amb peces en les quals hi forma part el vídeo, la fotogrfia i el codi baix el concepte.%0a*[['''John F. Simon Jr.'''->http://numeral.com/panels/panels.html]]:  Pioner en la utilització del codi per crear gràfics amb pantalles LCD amb programació.%0a*[['''John Maeda'''->http://www.maedastudio.com/index.php]]: Precursor de la utilització, la investigació en la creació del codi amb ordinador, entés com a mitjà creatiu per a dissenyadors i artistes. Destacar els seus textos i els seus estudis sobre "[[simplicity->http://lawsofsimplicity.com/]]".%0a*[['''Mary Flanagan'''->http://www.maryflanagan.com/imagesvideos]]: És una artista, productora, dissenyadora, tecnóloga, activista, escritora i teòrica la qual els seus treballs reflexen i integren tots aquests camps, amb instal.lacions basades en la xarxa, la interactivitat, el vídeo i el gràfic.%0a*[['''Casey Reas'''->http://reas.com/]]: Dissenyador i artista un dels creadors de Processing, els seus treballs destaquen per l'exploració i la relació entre l'art conceptual i software art.%0a*[['''Jared Tarbell'''->http://www.creativeapplications.net/flash/jared-tarbell-profile-events/]]: Artista, dissenyador que treballa amb codi sobretot amb la recursivitat com element principal de les seues creacions.%0a*[['''Ben Fry'''->http://benfry.com/projects/]]:La font del seu treball es la visualització de dades, emprant el color i la tipografia.%0a%0a!!!! Artist && Designers%0a*[['''Ivan Favalezza'''->https://ivanfavalezza.com/]]%0a*[['''Tyler Hobbs'''->https://tylerxhobbs.com/]]%0a* [['''Patrik Huebner'''->https://www.patrik-huebner.com/]]%0a* [['''Marcel Schwittlick'''->https://schwittlick.net//]]%0a* [['''Manolo Gamboa'''->http://manoloide.com/]]%0a* [['''Anders Hoff'''->https://inconvergent.net/]]%0a* [['''Matt Deslauriers'''->https://www.mattdesl.com/]]%0a* [['''Jonathan Puckey'''->https://www.jonathanpuckey.com/projects/typographic-rhythm/]]%0a* [['''Yining Shi'''->http://1023.io/web-development]]%0a* [[''' Saskia Freeke'''->http://www.sasj.nl/]]%0a* [['''Jürg Lehni'''->http://juerglehni.com/]]%0a* [['''Ishac Bertran'''->http://www.ishback.com/]]%0a* [['''Andreas Gysin'''->http://ertdfgcvb.com/]]%0a* [['''Clement Valla'''->http://clementvalla.com/]]%0a* [['''Anthony Antonellis'''->http://www.anthonyantonellis.com/]]%0a* [['''Ligia Duro'''->http://ligiaduro.com/]]%0a* [['''Stefanie Schwarz'''->http://www.stefanieschwarz-graphicdesign.de]]%0a* [['''Adam Ferris'''->http://www.adamferriss.com]]%0a* [['''Holger Lippmann '''->http://www.holgerlippmann.de/]]%0a* [['''Sergio Albiac '''->http://www.sergioalbiac.com/]]%0a* [['''Ilya Fridman '''->https://www.behance.net/ilyafridman]]%0a* [['''Luca Ferrairo'''->https://www.behance.net/wist]]%0a* [['''Matthieu Regout'''->http://www.matthieuregout.com/]]%0a* [['''Nicholas Taylor'''->http://nicholas-taylor.com/]]%0a* [['''Paolo Ceric''->https://www.behance.net/patakk]]%0a* [['''Aaron Koblin'''->http://www.aaronkoblin.com/]]%0a* [['''Alex Dragulescu'''->http://sq.ro/]]%0a* [['''Aranda Lasch'''->http://www.terraswarm.com/]]%0a* [['''ART+COM'''->http://www.artcom.de/]]%0a* [['''Fabio Lattanziantinori'''->http://fabiolattanziantinori.com/]]%0a* [['''Coralie Gourchechon'''->http://www.coraliegourguechon.fr/]]%0a* [['''Ted Davis'''->http://www.teddavis.org/]]%0a* [['''Ludwig Zeller'''->http://www.ludwigzeller.de/]]%0a* [['''Raquel Meyers'''->http://www.raquelmeyers.com/]]%0a* [['''Taeyoon Choi'''->http://taeyoonchoi.com/category/artworks/]]%0a* [['''Lionel Radisson'''->http://makio.free.fr/]]%0a* [['''Greg Borenstein'''->http://gregborenstein.com/]]%0a* [['''Kyuhashim'''->http://kyuhashim.com]]%0a* [['''Osamu Sato->https://archive.org/details/satoArtOfComputerDesigning/page/n19/mode/2up''']]%0a* [['''Golan Levin'''->https://vimeo.com/golanlevin]]%0a* [['''Yehwan Song'''->https://www.instagram.com/yehwan.yen.song/]]%0a* [['''Jessica Rosenkrantz'''->https://n-e-r-v-o-u-s.com/about_us.php]]%0a* [['''Marcel Schwittlick'''->https://schwittlick.net/]]%0a* [['''Universal Everything'''->https://www.universaleverything.com/]]%0a* [['''Robert Hodgin'''->https://roberthodgin.com/project/the-prow]]%0a* [['''Benedikt Groß'''->https://benedikt-gross.de/]]%0a* [['''Manfred Mohr'''->https://www.emohr.com/]]%0a%0a!!!! Estudis%0a* [['''Studiomoniker'''->https://studiomoniker.com/]]%0a* [['''Aeolab'''->http://www.aeolab.com/?s=projects]]%0a* [['''Open2Type'''->http://open2type.org/]]%0a* [['''Onformative'''->http://www.onformative.com/]]%0a* [['''Studio 2roqs'''->http://www.2roqs.fr]]%0a* [['''Free Art Bureau'''->http://freeartbureau.org]]%0a* [['''Yeohyun Ahn'''->http://www.yeoahn.com]]%0a* [['''Eno Henze'''->http://enohenze.de/]]%0a* [['''Normals'''->http://www.normalfutu.re/ ]]%0a* [['''Studio Batch '''->http://studiobatch.com/]]%0a* [['''Catalogtree 4.0'''->http://www.catalogtree.net/]]%0a* [['''Lust'''->http://lust.nl/]]%0a* [['''pangenerator'''->http://pangenerator.com]]%0a* [['''okdeluxe'''->http://www.okdeluxe.co.uk/]]%0a* [['''Brenda Waves'''->http://brendandawes.com/]]: data visualization%0a%0a!!!! Graphic computer design%0a* [['''triangulationblog -computerdesign'''->http://www.triangulationblog.com/2013/09/computer-graphics-art.html?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%253A+triangulati